reviewText: I always love the songs from this movie and haven't seen the movie until now.  Now I know why the music is so beautiful and touching.  Absolutely lovely movie for young couple.
Love this movie... Loved this movie so much I brought Aashiqui 2.

This was not the movie I thought I was ordering.  I thought I was ordering something that was much newer.  This movie is older than I thought.  I could immediately tell by the quality of the filming.  As I result I didn't finish watching it.  I know, I didn't even give it a chance.  I just wasn't interested.  I was too mad that I had ordered the wrong thing.
